::Zardus::

Zardus throws himself left, the missile shot by Kamodia exploding at his 
side, charring the right half of his body. The Alliance leader activates his 
jetpack, a bit surprized that it was still functional, and flies into the 
air, leaving Battera for Soundwave to deal with.
